        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>name</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The name of the class</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
The constructor register all provider tasks for metric updates by calling function registerMetricProvider provided by the power manager base class. The provider tasks are:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The shtcx task for temperature and humidity</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The battery manager task for battery metrics</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The HW metrics task for hardware metrics</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The data manager task for LTE metrics Afterwards it allocates the timer for initial boost on, inital LTE start delay and adxl wakeup to measurements transmission. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
